title: Bobby’s Beef with Carrie Underwood + First Dance Wedding Songs Fantasy Draft + Sister Hazel Stops By

description:
Bobby wonders if Carrie Underwood is trying to start a feud with him after she did an impression of him on the Country Top 30 Countdown. We do our first dance wedding songs fantasy draft. Plus, Sister Hazel stops by the studio to share new music.
